PrsnttnCpy verticalGutter\">These screws come with precise threaded and unthreaded <span class=\"Wrd\">portions,</span> allowing you to place only the stronger unthreaded portion <span class=\"Wrd\">(grip)</span> in joints subjected to sideways <span class=\"Wrd\">forces.</span> The flange distributes pressure where the screw meets the <span class=\"Wrd\">surface,</span> eliminating the need for a separate <span class=\"Wrd\">washer.</span> Made from <span class=\"Wrd\">18-8</span> stainless <span class=\"Wrd\">steel,</span> these screws have good chemical resistance and may be mildly <span class=\"Wrd\">magnetic.</span> Head height includes the <span class=\"Wrd\">flange.</span> Length is measured from under the <span class=\"Wrd\">flange.</span></p><p class=\"PrsnttnCpy\"><img class=\"Prsnttn_CADImg\" src=\"https://images1.mcmaster.com/mvB/Contents/gfx/CADIconForCpy.png?ver=1452869604\" width=\"22\" height=\"19\" alt=\"For technical drawings and 3-D models, click on a part number.\" />For technical drawings and 3-D models, click on a part number.</p></div>', '1406', 'Exact-Grip-Length--Flanged-Socket-Head-Screws', '', 'yes');
